2. **Any error messages or output you received**: This information is crucial for identifying issues and understanding the outcomes of your actions.
3. **The intended goal of the commands**: Knowing what you aimed to accomplish will allow me to provide more targeted feedback.

Once you provide this information, I can analyze it and offer insights, tips, and examples based on your experience with the Factorio REPL environment. Thank you!
